title: Are You Dreaming Too Small?
itunes:title: Are You Dreaming Too Small?
description:
When you think about your goals, do they scare the crap out of you or do you shoot small, so that you don't come up disappointed? Well in this episode, I will dive into big goals and small goals and help you change your mindset so that you can conquer the big goals!
